title: Fixed the old bug with the notification preference
message:
Fixed the old bug with the notification preference

The problem was that sharedPrefs.getBoolean() called inside the
onPreferenceChange doesn’t have the latest changes.
So when a preference change before Android calls onPreferenceChange and
then it saves the variable on the SharedPreferences
